_sText:
This is the brandnew he_tennis map of the year 2008!


Check out some features:

+ Walk into the floodlight to get a new he-grenade!

+ Nomore lags caused by too many grenades on the ground or flying around in the map!

+ Throw grenades everywhere! But you still cannot walk onto the other teams side ;)

+ Nice ambience: tenniscourt in a gym hall.
